data.description: Welcome Home! This adorable, move in ready home is situated on an oversized lot located on a quiet street  with mature trees shading this nice yard. This convenient location is close to shopping and restaurants. The  3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home features new vinyl flooring, new interior and exterior paint, updated  bathrooms, lighting and more. This great home is a perfect starter home or a great investment home.  Located approximately 2 miles from Lake Cannon. Lake Cannon is an incredible entertainment lake with  public boat ramps, fishing, viewing the awesome wildlife and enjoying a picnic lunch. Why rent when you  can own!!!! Call me today to set an appointment to view.
